Package: curvehashd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Curvehash is a crypto-currency project forked from Bitcoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original Bitcoin's
 preferable properties.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, curvehashd, and the CLI tool
 curvehash-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: curvehash-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Curvehash is a crypto-currency project forked from Bitcoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original Bitcoin's
 preferable properties.
 .
 This package provides Curvehash-Qt, a GUI client for Curvehash based on Qt.

Package: curvehash-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 Curvehash is a crypto-currency project forked from Bitcoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original Bitcoin's
 preferable properties.
 This package provides curvehash-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a curvehash daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
